      <text xml:space="preserve">{{About|the stringed musical instrument}}
{{Infobox instrument
|name=Cello
|names=Violoncello
|image=Cello front side.png
|image_capt=Cello, front and side view
|background=string
|hornbostel_sachs=321.322-71
|hornbostel_sachs_desc=Composite [[chordophone]] sounded by a [[bow (music)|bow]]
|developed=about 1660 from the [[bass violin]]
|range=[[Image:Range cello.png|130px|center]]
|related=
