      <comment>/* Death and legacy */ expand caption; the sculpture is not 'on' the cemetery</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox artist
| bgcolour      = #6495ED
| name          = Constantin Brâncuşi
| image         = Edward Steichen - Brancusi.jpg
| imagesize     = 200px
| caption       = Constantin Brâncuşi; Photograph taken by [[Edward Steichen]] in 1922.
| birthname     =
| birthdate     = {{birth date|1876|2|19}}
| birth_place   = [[Peştişani|Hobiţa]], [[Romania]]
| deathdate     = {{death date and age|1957|3|16|1876|2|19}}
| deathplace    = [[Paris, France]]
| resting_place = [[Cimetière du Montparnasse]] Paris
| nationality   = [[Romanians|Romanian]], [[French people|French]] (after 1952)
| field         = [[Sculpture]]
| training      = [[École des Beaux-Arts]]
