*Province of [[Amorgos]] - Amorgos
*Province of [[Santorini|Thera]] - Thera
''Note:'' Provinces no longer hold any legal status in [[Greece]].


==Sailing in the Cyclades==
The Cyclades, like the other Aegean island groups, are exposed to the north/north east, putting them in the path of the [[Meltemi|Meltemi wind]] that can reach [[Beaufort scale|Force]] 7 and above. The Meltemi tends to start in late June and will come and go until September.

