      <comment>Added external links, added other families as per Wikispecies, removed {{storks}}</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Taxobox
|name = Ciconiiformes
|fossil_range = Late [[Eocene]] to Recent
|image = Saddle-Billed_Stork.jpg
|image_width = 240px
|image_caption = An adult [[Saddle-billed Stork]]
|regnum = [[Animal]]ia
|phylum = [[Chordate|Chordata]]
|classis = [[bird|Aves]]
|infraclassis = [[Neognathae]]
|ordo = '''Ciconiiformes'''
|ordo_authority = [[Charles Lucien Jules Laurent Bonaparte|Bonaparte]], 1854
|subdivision_ranks = Families
